  "identifier": "HB 343",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to contributions made to a Kentucky qualified expense program.",
  "abstract": "Create a new section to KRS Chapter 141 to provide employers a tax credit for contributions to an employee's Kentucky Educational Savings Plan Trust account or STABLE Kentucky account; amend KRS 141.0205 to specify ordering of the credit; amend KRS 131.190 to allow the Department of Revenue to report on the credit.",
